name: gryds
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "gryds" %}
{% set version = "0.0.9" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/gryds-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a06c16d63554aff846e5bec4a6d9126c1a6a71e9f45e0eae5dce63ec8ceb5c66

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - numpy
    - python >=3.6
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - gryds
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/MBPhys/gryds
  summary: 'Gryds: a Python package for geometric transformations of images'
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/napari
